					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The registers are write only, and cannot be read back.  So writing to 2005 or 2006 will make changes to the state of the PPU, and 2005 and 2006 can not be read back.<br />There's lots of more details about scrolling, and it's been posted to death on the boards and wiki already.</div>

					
